quran[9{c,v,t}:
41,12,"tab uss ne do din ke andar saat aasman bana diye, aur har aasman mein uss ka qanoon wahi kar diya aur aasman duniya ko hum ne charaghoon se aaraasta kya aur usay khoob mehfooz kar diya yeh sab kuch aik zabardast Aleem hasti ka mansoobah hai"
41,13,ab agar yeh log mun morty hain to inn se keh do ke mein tum ko usi terhan ke aik achanak toot parney walay azaab se darata hon jaissa Aad aur smod par nazil howa tha
41,14,"jab khuda ke rasool unn ke paas agay aur peechay, har taraf se aeye aur inhen samjhaya ke Allah ke siwa kisi ki bandagi nah karo to unhon ne kaha"" hamara rab chahta to farishtay bhejta, lehaza hum uss baat ko nahi mantay jis ke liye tum beje gay ho """
41,15,"Aad ka haal yeh tha ke woh zameen mein kisi haq ke baghair barray ban baithy aur kehnay lagey"" kon hai hum se ziyada zor aawar"" unn ko yeh nah soojha ke jis khuda ne un ko peda kya hai woh un se ziyada zor aawar hai? woh hamari ayaat ka inkaar hi karte rahay"
41,16,"aakhir kaar hum ne chand manhoos dinon mein sakht tofani howa un par bhaij di taakay inhen duniya hi ki zindagi mein zillat o ruswai ke azaab ka maza chakkha den, aur akhirat ka azaab to is se bhi ziyada ruswa kin hai, wahan koi un ki madad karne wala nah ho ga"
41,17,"rahay smod, to un ke samnay hum ne raah raast paish ki magar unhon ne rasta dekhnay ke bajaye andha bana rehna pasand kya aakhir unn ke krtoton ki badolat zillat ka azaab unn par toot para"
41,18,aur hum ne unn logon ko bacha liya jo imaan laaye thay aur gumraahi o bad amli se parhaiz karte thay
41,19,aur zara uss waqt ka khayaal karo jab Allah ke yeh dushman dozakh ki taraf jaane ke liye ghair laaye jayen ge unn ke uglo ko pichlon ke anay taq rok rakha jaye ga
41,20,phir jab sab wahan poanch jayen ge to un ke kaan aur un ki ankhen aur un ke jism ki khalin un par gawahi den gi ke woh duniya mein kya kuch karte rahay hain
